<section class="page dark-page">
  <h1>RAK47 Achievements</h1>

  <p>
    RAK47 is built from both musicianship and production. Before the producer
    name, there was percussion, marching band, discipline, music theory, and
    performance experience.
  </p>

  <div class="achievement-grid">

    <div class="achievement-card">
      <h2>Percussion Background</h2>
      <p>
        Rakim Spriggs developed his foundation through percussion performance,
        learning rhythm, timing, control, dynamics, technique, and musical
        discipline through school and collegiate band environments.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="achievement-card">
      <h2>Lithonia High School</h2>
      <p>
        Percussion and marching band experience helped build the foundation for
        live performance, cadence, timing, ensemble awareness, and the discipline
        needed to perform as part of a larger musical unit.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="achievement-card">
      <h2>Georgia State University</h2>
      <p>
        Experience connected to Georgia State University strengthened Rakim's
        understanding of collegiate-level musicianship, performance standards,
        rhythm structure, and organized musical preparation.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="achievement-card">
      <h2>Hampton University</h2>
      <p>
        Exposure to Hampton University's symphonic and marching band culture
        contributed to Rakim's knowledge of arrangement, musicianship,
        performance discipline, and percussion-centered sound.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="achievement-card">
      <h2>Music Theory</h2>
      <p>
        RAK47 applies music theory through rhythm, arrangement, structure,
        tempo, melody, dynamics, and the relationship between percussion and
        emotional movement in a record.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="achievement-card">
      <h2>Percussion Teaching Methods</h2>
      <p>
        Rakim understands percussion teaching methods including repetition,
        rudiments, timing drills, call-and-response instruction, ensemble
        listening, stick control, hand technique, and gradual skill development.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="achievement-card">
      <h2>Producer Credits</h2>
      <p>
        As RAK47, Rakim has produced records with major underground traction,
        including known songs with Lil Meat that have reached over one million
        streams.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="achievement-card">
      <h2>Creative Direction</h2>
      <p>
        Beyond beat-making, RAK47 brings a full creative approach to music:
        production, branding, photography, artist development, arrangement,
        sound selection, and visual identity.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

